---
title: New Zealand’s Chicken & Couscous Salad Top recipes from HelloFresh markets around the world
description: In honor of the summer games, we’re going global with this gold medal winner from HF New Zealand! Go the distance with this fresh, savory salad bowl that starts with springy, tender couscous. You’ll stir in fresh spinach and sweet roasted carrots, then top with succulent seared chicken seasoned with savory spices. Finish with a sprinkle of toasted walnuts and a creamy drizzle of garlic aioli.
